<conjf>Perwigged</conjf> <pr>(p⟦ecr⟧r"⟦icr⟧*w⟦icr⟧gd)</pr>; <pos>p. pr.
& vb. n.</pos> <conjf>Perwigging</conjf>
<pr>(p⟦ecr⟧r"⟦icr⟧*w⟦icr⟧g*g⟦icr⟧ng)</pr>.]</vmorph> <def>To dress with
a periwig, or with false hair.</def> <rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>periwigged</ent>⟦br⟧
